06:54.460 --> 07:01.400
I was sent to Sunday School when I was very little and I came interested in the Bible and I read it on my own.

07:02.240 --> 07:05.280
And I even read the Book of Mormon, which was about nine years old.

07:06.620 --> 07:18.060
